OL,3,C33-year-old man arrested in connection
OL,4,Cwith night club bomb threat
OL,6,FA 33-year old man has been arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with an incident at a
OL,8,FGuernsey night club where a bomb
OL,9,Fthreat was made.
OL,11,FPolice say the threat was made in the
OL,12,Fearly hours of this morning at Folies
OL,13,Fin St Peter Port but add that,
OL,14,Ffollowing investigations, there was no
OL,15,Fbomb.
OL,17,FEnquiries are ongoing but officers say
OL,18,Fthey have now been able to remove the
OL,19,Fpolice cordon on the North Plantation
OL,20,Fwhich is now accessible to the public
OL,21,Fagain.
